General.Name: ARK Resources Bhd
General.Description: ARK Resources Holdings Berhad, an investment holding company, engages in civil, building construction, and engineering works in Malaysia. The company operates through Property Development, Construction, and Management and Investment Holding segments. It undertakes civil and geo-technical engineering, mechanical and electrical engineering, and turnkey construction works. The company also engages in the property development business, as well as the provision of management services. ARK Resources Holdings Berhad was founded in 1983 and is based in Bayan Lepas, Malaysia.
